    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "七聖召喚",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決闘対戦",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "ステージ紹介",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "キャッツテールからこの「七聖召喚」界を征服しようとする伝説のプレイヤー。キャッツテールで自分に見合う相手を探している。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【ヒント】腕の立つプレイヤーのため、ランクがもう少し高くなってからまた挑みましょう。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "相手の編成",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3198,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/194600931/6c1a40b971633c08f8f376ce5bc61f7c_2210314723212520086.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "ヒルチャール・岩兜の王",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3181,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/194600931/1692ce668a14a238e1fa6b763b9ae0ce_5034368879662393783.png",
